			"content_html": "<p>“You might think that the G.O.P. would eventually learn …, realize that tax cuts aren’t magical, and come up with some different ideas. But … it’s difficult for a man to understand something when his campaign contributions depend on his not understanding it.” —<a href=\"https://nyti.ms/2KqKFow\">Paul Krugman</a></p>\n",
